There are some popular and sweet foods you eat on a regular basis that can cause harm or damage your health if you continue to eat them every day but many people around the world don’t know about these foods. So, in this article, I’ll educate you on some of the bad foods you eat on a daily basis that can harm your body.
1. One of the foods that you eat on a regular basis is ice cream. Ice cream is mostly eaten by children and few adults around the world but this food contains enough added sugar that can cause harm to your body in the near future if you continue to eat it regularly. You are advised to cut down the rate at which you eat it regularly and also try your best to visit a medical doctor for a regular medical checkup.
2. Another food that you eat every day which can cause harm to your body is noodles Because noodles contain chemical preservatives that can cause harm to the body. It also has low nutritional content.
3. Another food which can cause harm to your health is baked foods Because they contain saturated fat that can increase your body cholesterol level which can lead to serious heart problems in the near future if you don’t cut down the rate at which you consume them.


